{"id":"SHENSHENGDEBEIXIJU18","scripts":[{"dir":1,"say":"もうチートだと言われてもしょうがないわね…あの砲撃は…","nameColor":"#ff5c5c","bgm":"battle-boss-italy","side":2,"expression":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":603020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ロイヤルの最高の騎士のひとり、ウォースパイトが戦いに勝利した。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"side":2,"dir":1,"say":"夜なのに、なんであんなに正確に撃てるのよ！","actor":900197,"nameColor":"#ff5c5c"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"くっ…旧式の戦艦と侮ったツケね…！","side":2,"expression":1,"dir":1,"actor":603020,"nameColor":"#ff5c5c"},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"ふふ、このウォースパイト、戦いで学んだことを一つ教えてあげるわ","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"それは、艦船の性能の違いが、戦力の決定的差ではないということよ","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":3,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"己のカンレキにこだわるのではなく、戦士としての初心のまま困難に挑み、そして絶えず切磋琢磨し続ける――","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":4,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"それこそがロイヤルの強さよ。ふん、そちらさえ良ければ、このウォースパイト、少し指導してあげても――","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"…………","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":5,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"…………行ったわね","nameColor":"#a9f548","action":[{"y":30,"x":0,"dur":0.15,"delay":0,"number":2,"type":"shake"}],"side":2,"expression":6,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,